Text:
Did you see that?  Shush, get down!  Over there, behind that burning car-must be 6 of them headed over next door.  What, didn't you call 911 already it's been an 15 minutes and still no cops?!  Okay, okay, get ready-make sure they are inside before...   

When seconds count and your life is in the balance, the police are minutes away...  

Thanks for all the uploads!!
